text:
Are you suffering from health anxiety? Here are 3 tips to overcome it ⬆️

It’s natural to experience some level of concern about your health. But excessively worrying, frequently visiting your doctor, or spending hours online researching symptoms is counterproductive as it feeds the health anxiety.

If you spend excessive time worrying and seeking reassurance from others about your symptoms, there are several strategies you can use to break free. As a therapist, here are my 3 top tips - 

1️⃣ Recognise
2️⃣ Stop feeding the pattern
3️⃣ Focus on calming your nervous system
.
